--- Test Coverage ---
Unit tests (oms_writer_test.go):
- TestIsValidOMSTransition_HappyPath: 7 valid transitions verified
- TestIsValidOMSTransition_RejectPaths: 3 rejection paths verified
- TestIsValidOMSTransition_Invalid: 7 invalid transitions verified as blocked
- TestOrderLifecycleFullPath: full NEW→VALIDATED→RISK_APPROVED→SUBMITTED end-to-end

--- State Machine Coverage ---
Happy path: NEW → VALIDATED → RISK_APPROVED → SUBMITTED → WORKING → PARTIALLY_FILLED → FILLED
Rejection: VALIDATED → REJECTED | RISK_APPROVED → REJECTED | SUBMITTED → FAILED
Cancellation: SUBMITTED/WORKING → CANCELLED
Expiry: SUBMITTED/WORKING → EXPIRED

